%N A392841 Number of trailing zeros in a type of Zeckendorf expansion based on the Fibonacci numbers of odd index.
%C A392841 This sequence is the limit, as k goes to infinity, of the finite sequences (A035614(F(2k+1)-i), i=2..F(2k+1)), where F(k) = A000045(k) is the k-th Fibonacci number.
%C A392841 Here are the first few such finite sequences:
%C A392841   k=1: 0
%C A392841   k=2: 0, 2, 1, 0
%C A392841   k=3: 0, 2, 1, 0, 4, 1, 0, 3, 0, 2, 1, 0
%Y A392841 Cf. A035614, A392842, A001519, A000045.
%K A392841 nonn
%O A392841 1,2
